---

<section class="quality-pledge-section" id="quality">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-badge">我们的承诺</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">透明、开放、可信赖</h2>
      <p class="section-description">
        我们深信，开源项目的长久发展建立在透明和信任之上
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="pledge-grid">
      <div class="pledge-card">
        <div class="pledge-icon-wrapper">
          <div class="pledge-icon">🔍</div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="pledge-title">完全开源</h3>
        <p class="pledge-description">
          代码完整托管于 GitHub，接受社区审查。不隐藏任何核心逻辑，您可以深入了解每一行代码的实现细节。
        </p>
        <div class="pledge-links">
          <a href="https://github.com/smartboot/smart-servlet" target="_blank" class="pledge-link">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/>
            </svg>
            浏览代码
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pledge-card">
        <div class="pledge-icon-wrapper">
          <div class="pledge-icon">📝</div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="pledge-title">文档完善</h3>
        <p class="pledge-description">
          提供详尽的安装指南、API 文档和最佳实践。从入门到精通，每个阶段都有清晰的技术文档支持。
        </p>
        <div class="pledge-links">
          <a href="./guides/about/" class="pledge-link">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg>
            查看文档
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pledge-card">
        <div class="pledge-icon-wrapper">
          <div class="pledge-icon">🧪</div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="pledge-title">测试透明</h3>
        <p class="pledge-description">
          性能测试方法、TCK 测试报告全部公开。您可以复现所有测试结果，确保数据的真实性和可信度。
        </p>
        <div class="pledge-links">
          <a href="./guides/tck_report/" class="pledge-link">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="16" x2="8" y1="13" y2="13"/><line x1="16" x2="8" y1="17" y2="17"/><polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"/></svg>
            TCK 报告
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pledge-card">
        <div class="pledge-icon-wrapper">
          <div class="pledge-icon">🤝</div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="pledge-title">社区支持</h3>
        <p class="pledge-description">
          活跃的开发者社区，Gitee Issues 及时响应。您的问题和建议都会被认真对待，共同推进项目发展。
        </p>
        <div class="pledge-links">
          <a href="https://gitee.com/smartboot/smart-servlet/issues" target="_blank" class="pledge-link">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
            问题反馈
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .quality-pledge-section {
    padding: 6rem 1rem;
    background: var(--bg-primary);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3);
    border-radius: 9999px;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #f59e0b;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  :root[data-theme="light"] .section-badge {
    background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.08);
    border-color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.2);
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .section-description {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .pledge-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .pledge-card {
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .pledge-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: var(--border-hover);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  :root[data-theme="light"] .pledge-card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .pledge-icon-wrapper {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .pledge-icon {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6, #8b5cf6);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
  }

  .pledge-title {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
  }

  .pledge-description {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .pledge-links {
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  .pledge-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    color: #3b82f6;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .pledge-link:hover {
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .pledge-link svg {
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }

  .pledge-link:hover svg {
    transform: translateX(2px);
  }

  /* 协议信息 */
  .license-info {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding: 1.75rem 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.08), rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.08));
    border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
    border-radius: 1rem;
  }

  .license-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .license-content {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .license-content h4 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .license-content p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .license-note {
    color: var(--accent-primary);
  }

  .license-link {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.375rem;
    padding: 0.625rem 1.25rem;
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    color: #3b82f6;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    white-space: nowrap;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .license-link:hover {
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.25);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .license-link svg {
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }

  .license-link:hover svg {
    transform: translateX(3px);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .quality-pledge-section {
      padding: 4rem 1rem;
    }

    .pledge-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .license-info {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .license-content {
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>